Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.23,line,,0,0,0,,勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:13.27,line,,0,0,0,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:17.33,line,,0,0,0,,我是赞州中学勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.96,line,,0,0,0,,勇者，结城友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:40.13,line,,0,0,0,,传达到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:56.85,line,,0,0,0,,活下去！
